{"tid":148380,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[NO POO] 有無人剩係用清水洗頭","createTime":"2017-03-08T14:35:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-05T21:50:12.000Z","uid":2023,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"060128081776768b9a5f88d00fb7fcb538ed52c2","tid":148380,"uid":2023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T14:35:40.000Z","msg":"每日梳頭, 沖涼唔用洗頭水洗頭<br />\n頭個2-5日個頭會好油,好痕同好硬<br />\n每日梳頭都梳左勁多污糟野出黎<br />\n到今日為止無用洗頭水3個禮拜<br />\n頭髮唔痕唔乾岩岩好, 但仲係好硬(應該無辦法, 始終用洗頭水護髮素一定柔順D)"},{"pid":"45151ab706ba0e79965102a201d6b80047ede78a","tid":148380,"uid":2023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T14:48:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c3adef9890882d7479fdc39ebab289681e04543","tid":148380,"uid":85377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T15:03:18.000Z","msg":"Ching 水點去油"},{"pid":"6ceab10c559b04ee0acaeb2ed14bb02dade02fec","tid":148380,"uid":2023,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T15:08:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Ching 水點去油</blockquote><br />\n點會去唔到..."},{"pid":"a3343b1b4474d3cbacbcacc2a7a55902e679c085","tid":148380,"uid":9942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T15:10:17.000Z","msg":"之前試過 伏到仆街"},{"pid":"d016c541c0fd5fec76e7799aa0b63f7df4cb92ad","tid":148380,"uid":2023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T15:18:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前試過 伏到仆街</blockquote><br />\n可以點伏法???<br />\n我而家完全無問題WO<br />\n甩頭髮都少左"},{"pid":"a223eb0b3e0583dd7f84ea115130adf62cd83a80","tid":148380,"uid":57594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T15:22:40.000Z","msg":"面粉去油都唔錯，天然d一茶匙醋 兌開麵糊水洗頭都幾好"},{"pid":"a072f44df10b4500e7229dccfd265c6dfe6f27f3","tid":148380,"uid":80294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T17:29:02.000Z","msg":"學古人用木灰 米水 洗"},{"pid":"14f864b03d30a39f1be4d9eda7f52adf7485717a","tid":148380,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T17:31:28.000Z","msg":"用開乾洗"},{"pid":"60b37e87fe4e559fabba0bcaf7ac7e51008ca463","tid":148380,"uid":85567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T17:54:13.000Z","msg":"我都想淨係用清水 但開頭個頭仲未習慣個段時間會好難頂"},{"pid":"91d42bf315044816947ab95a154f7cb19c012254","tid":148380,"uid":65721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T18:45:19.000Z","msg":"為咩？"},{"pid":"8c8fa271b11e9fad8f4bde72ee0a3007eef71905","tid":148380,"uid":42949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T18:59:11.000Z","msg":"我每星期用一次洗頭水<br />\n我成日有頭皮<br />\n試左一排又好似冇乜"},{"pid":"db0805ccf15f006ce55473ec2025e19ff7f0c667","tid":148380,"uid":2023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T01:37:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>為咩？</blockquote><br />\n第一，洗頭水啲化學物質對頭皮有害<br />\n第二，其實頭皮適當出油係保護同清潔作用，但現代人日日用洗頭水洗走啲油，令到個頭以為頭油不足而大量分泌頭油，所以啲人一日唔洗頭就會超油<br />\n第三，慳錢<br />\n第四，我唔想個頭咁乾又或者太油"},{"pid":"139f2cc899cf8610e05f10caac9428f06c03cd22","tid":148380,"uid":30663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T15:42:31.000Z","msg":"半頭無用洗頭水了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個人覺得好左 個頭唔會油得好緊要 係正常既油份<br />\n以前啲頭髮硬到髮型師都剪到卡較剪 日日起身都鋼線刷咁款 依家明顯柔順左好多 唔整頭都唔會豎晒出黎"},{"pid":"65e3d03f845026031b1d36d4aa973e31ca64108f","tid":148380,"uid":2023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T16:12:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都想淨係用清水 但開頭個頭仲未習慣個段時間會好難頂</blockquote><br />\n好快會習慣"},{"pid":"162f22159d759625856a50bd03dccf327a8b388d","tid":148380,"uid":12448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T19:01:36.000Z","msg":"巴打淨係清水洗會唔會頭痕？<br />\n<br />\n我都好想試 但係一唔攞shampoo洗到個頭乾乾淨淨<br />\n瞓覺就會痕到仆街 R到頭皮出囇血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35003e7b598a0455e8785bb0854ffc41800387eb","tid":148380,"uid":35457,